{
  "stem": "3757.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a very nice nurse, but everybody hated her, because she was always looking at what the cleaning women do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I work like from the morning to the evening, because it was the best not to talk-- so little to talk as you can.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I told her that this-- I don't know why this-- her-- she-- this-- this nurse, why they were yelling at me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I incidentally used that bathroom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she didn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The next day-- I-- this was a-- a three-story building, and I was just cleaning up in the-- upper floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nurse calls, Irene.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Here are two people from the party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have their own Nazi party in the sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And before that, they tried to convince me to join the party.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- I never cared for politics, and I don't do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But here, I have to put in something else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were three men in the-- in the big building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they-- they worked in the garden-- were a big garden there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I came down from that to the-- my building, they always, they're looking at me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I saw that they talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I thought that I was a young, not bad-looking girl, that they talk about [LAUGHS] me something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I heard that these three are Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they-- that-- that time, a lot of Polish people escaped to Hungary from the German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they-- the story was that they were soldiers-- Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they fought against the German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the German army-- army came in, then they escaped to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I don't know how they got to this sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So-- and this I put in between, because later, I come back to this.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
